{
  "id": "adv_card_suz_12_01",
  "title": "成宮すず",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "アリス！　私がアリスですわよ！\n『劇団★見』の主演ですわよ！",
      "startTime": 4.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "聞いたぞ。今度のライブで、雫とすずのダブル主演で\n不思議の国のアリスがモチーフの舞台を演じるんだよな",
      "startTime": 12.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "でも……大丈夫か？\n演技の経験は、以前連ドラに出演した一回きりだろう",
      "startTime": 18.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "今や私はBIG4！　つまりは大女優成宮すずですわ！\n不安は捨てて大船に乗った気持ちでいてくださいまし！",
      "startTime": 29.7611111004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "随分と大きく出たな\n大女優はさすがに言い過ぎじゃないか……？",
      "startTime": 37.0333282471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "細かいことを言わないでくださいまし\n私のこの自信は過信ではありませんのよ",
      "startTime": 43.8558907191,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "なぜならこの私、不思議の国のアリスならば\n幼い頃に劇で演じたことがあるんですから！",
      "startTime": 52.6558907191,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだったのか……\nそれでその劇はどうだったんだ？　好評だったのか？",
      "startTime": 59.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、当然ですわ！\n私が出たおかげであの劇は大成功したのですから！",
      "startTime": 65.9958904902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "舞台の真ん中に堂々と立って、燦然と輝く私に\n観客はみんな、釘付けでしたの！",
      "startTime": 76.4958859125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "終幕と共に浴びせられる大喝采……\nスタンディングオベーションする観客達の姿！",
      "startTime": 83.6625571568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "あの輝かしい成功は忘れられませんの\n今もあの景色が目に浮かびますわ",
      "startTime": 92.1292258579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ、当時の私と出会っていなかったのが\n本当に惜しいですわね、{user}さん",
      "startTime": 100.7625591913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……もう既にアリス役を演じていたのか\n心配は杞憂だったみたいだな",
      "startTime": 109.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "ん……アリス役？",
      "startTime": 112.3177082061,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ、ビデオか何かに記録は残っていないのか？\n優や琴乃、雫の参考になるかもしれないし……",
      "startTime": 119.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　い、いや、残念なことにお父様も\nお母様も感動のあまり録画を忘れていまして",
      "startTime": 127.4546284357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、それは残念だ……\nでも、今思えばぴったりの配役だな",
      "startTime": 134.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "確かにすずの髪型や雰囲気も\nどことなくアリスに似ている気がするよ",
      "startTime": 140.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "え、えっと、そ、そうですわ！\nもはやアリス役は私の天命ですの！",
      "startTime": 147.7252521197,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "動きが多くて大変な役だと思っていたが\n穴に落ちる演技も経験済みなら安心だな",
      "startTime": 155.1333272298,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "えーっと、あ、ああ！\nウサギの穴に飛び込むシーンですわよね？",
      "startTime": 162.1010065078,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "あんなのぴょーんですわ！\nふわっとしてぴょんぴょーんですの！　余裕ですわ！",
      "startTime": 167.6010258357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　どうしたすず。やけに汗をかいている\n気がするんだが、具合でも悪いのか？",
      "startTime": 175.9990207463,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "え、えっと、そ、そうですわね……\n練習の疲れが出てしまったのかも……",
      "startTime": 183.6210282326,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10799.989318900003,
          "startTime": 194.4210175515
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "今日はもう失礼いたしますわね\nアリス役、この成宮すずに任せてくださいまし！",
      "startTime": 189.7876948993,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "すず、どうしたんだ……？\nゆっくり休んでくれればいいんだが",
      "startTime": 198.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後、劇団★見の練習終わりにて",
      "startTime": 202.689155348,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1933.336385299981,
          "startTime": 204.6224917333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1933.336385299981,
          "startTime": 204.6224917333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 204.4224937676
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あら、様子を見に来ましたの……？\nこの通り、アリス役の練習は順調ですわよ",
      "startTime": 210.4510341646,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "いや、雫について一つ相談があってな……\n実は雫もアリスの劇に出たことがあるそうなんだ",
      "startTime": 218.8666646322,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、その時に演じたのが木の役だったそうで、今回の\nアリス役は勝手が違うと苦戦しているみたいなんだよ",
      "startTime": 226.8666646322,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz018.m4a",
      "text": "雫も木の役を演じていましたの……！？\nこ、こほん。木の役を馬鹿にしてはいけませんわ！",
      "startTime": 235.0042320889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz019.m4a",
      "text": "ずーっと立っていなければならないですし\n衣装の葉っぱが顔を掠めてむず痒いんですのよ",
      "startTime": 243.4042320889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz020.m4a",
      "text": "あれを演じることはもはや一種の職人技\n普通の人じゃ演じきれない大役ですわ！",
      "startTime": 252.4042188646,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "ず、随分詳しいんだな……\nまるで木の役の経験者みたいだが……",
      "startTime": 258.8666646322,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_12_01-suz021.m4a",
      "text": "あ、こ、これは……そう！\n当時木の役を演じていた友達に聞いたんですのよ！",
      "startTime": 266.0852844557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
